RE:INSTEAD links with the following libraries/sources:

    Lua (MIT)
    SDL2 (zlib)
    stb libraries (Public Domain)
    lite editor (MIT)

RE:INSTEAD _may_ be linked with:

    freetype 2 (FTL)
    libschrift (ISC)
    Tolk (as windows dll) (LGPLv3)

RE:INSTEAD uses dictionary files from the http://aot.ru project that is
covered by the terms of the LGPL license. See data/stead3/morph/COPYING.

The source code includes games in 'data/games' dir that are distributed
under the CC BY-SA 4.0 license. See data/games/COPYING.
